<details class="faq-item"><summary>How quickly can we start?<span class="fi">+</span></summary><div class="faq-body">1-3 business days. Ship inventory &rarr; we receive and barcode &rarr; start fulfilling next day.</div></details>
<details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you handle international shipping?<span class="fi">+</span></summary><div class="faq-body">We specialize in domestic Ukrainian fulfillment via Nova Poshta. For international, we prepare parcels for your carrier.</div></details>
<details class="faq-item"><summary>What integrations are available?<span class="fi">+</span></summary><div class="faq-body">Rozetka, Prom.ua, Kasta, WooCommerce, OpenCart, Horoshop. CRM: KeyCRM, SalesDrive. REST API and Webhook.</div></details>
<details class="faq-item"><summary>Is there a language barrier?<span class="fi">+</span></summary><div class="faq-body">No. English-speaking team. Dedicated account manager via Telegram, email, or phone.</div></details>
